WEBVTT

1
01:04:04.910 --> 01:04:08.590 
把他们的会面记下来  说的每个字都要
Let's document all their meetings. Keep full details.

2
01:04:09.790 --> 01:04:11.920 
我敢说  这儿风景真好
One could dare say it's beautiful here.

3
01:04:11.960 --> 01:04:13.760 
倾听叶落的声音
Listen to the leaves scratch the air.

4
01:04:14.420 --> 01:04:19.180 
有时候听着像枪支开火  有时候像
Sometimes it sounds like gunfire and sometimes like...

5
01:04:19.220 --> 01:04:21.760 
- 像鼓掌吗  - 是啊  鼓掌
Like applause? - Yes, applause.

6
01:04:26.050 --> 01:04:27.250 
默里先生好了
Mr. Murray.

7
01:04:27.250 --> 01:04:29.810 
我也该走了
All right, I should be off then.

8
01:04:30.190 --> 01:04:31.610 
记得查看信箱
Check your post.

9
01:04:31.650 --> 01:04:34.230 
我会再记下我的想法  为你抛砖引玉
I will garner my thoughts and spark them off to yours.

10
01:04:34.270 --> 01:04:35.520 
剑刃互利
Cause iron sharpens iron.

11
01:04:35.520 --> 01:04:38.320 
一个人在和友人交谈时才会更有想法
So one man sharpens the 【countness】 of a friend.

